1) Name different forms of communication.
Ans. Different forms of communication are:
i) Verbal Communication
ii) Non-verbal Communication
iii) Written Communication
iv) Visual Communication

2) Discuss the pros and cons of;

a) Verbal/oral communication
Ans. Pros of verbal communication are:
i) We can express our felling properly
ii) We can get better feedback
iii) No money is used for it
iv) Faster way of communication

Cons of verbal communication are:
i) Some one can fell anxiety or shy
ii) They need to be in one place and can not do from a long distance or any part of the world

b) Non-verbal communication
Ans. Pros of non-verbal communincation are:
i) Someone can understand your message more easily
